          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1708421411499-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>South Indian-style hake cashew curry</strong> with the <strong>cardamom rice </strong>(discard the cardamom pods!)</p><p>Garnish with your <strong>crispy onions</strong>, <strong>reserved</strong> <strong>chopped coriander</strong> and <strong>reserved chopped</strong> <strong>chilli</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
